1088
01:20:34.772 --> 01:20:36.440
Que Dieu vous bénisse !

1089
01:20:38.776 --> 01:20:41.236
RÉPONSE AUTOMATIQUE AUX PRIÈRES...

1090
01:20:41.612 --> 01:20:44.949
